    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Male holotype of Boophis baetkei sp. n. (ZSM 2051 / 2007) in life. A. Dorsolateral view, B. Ventral view. SVL 30.8 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/182844/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182845>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. A. Male paratype of Boophis baetkei sp. n. (ZSM 1638 / 2008) in life, lateral aspect of head. Note lack of dorsolateral stripe on posterior body. B. Audiospectrogram and corresponding waveform of the advertisement call of Boophis baetkei sp. n., emitted by the holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/182845/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

